{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"react-grid---searching\"><a href=\"#react-grid---searching\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>React Grid - Searching</h1>\n<p>The Grid component supports searching data programmatically or using the value an end user types in the corresponding Search Panel editor.</p>\n<h2 id=\"related-plugins\"><a href=\"#related-plugins\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Related Plugins</h2>\n<p>The following plugins implement the searching feature:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"../reference/search-state.md\">SearchState</a> - controls the search state</li>\n<li><a href=\"../reference/integrated-filtering.md\">IntegratedFiltering</a> - performs built-in data searching and filtering</li>\n<li><a href=\"../reference/toolbar.md\">Toolbar</a> - renders the Grid Toolbar</li>\n<li><a href=\"../reference/search-panel.md\">SearchPanel</a> - renders the search panel</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Note that <a href=\"./plugin-overview.md#plugin-order\">plugin order</a> is important.</p>\n<h2 id=\"basic-setup\"><a href=\"#basic-setup\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Basic Setup</h2>\n<p>Import the plugins listed above to set up a Grid with basic searching.</p>\n<h3 id=\"uncontrolled-mode\"><a href=\"#uncontrolled-mode\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Uncontrolled Mode</h3>\n<p>In the <a href=\"controlled-and-uncontrolled-modes.md\">uncontrolled mode</a>, specify the initial searching value in the <code>SearchState</code> plugin's <code>defaultValue</code> property.</p>\n<p>.embedded-demo({ \"path\": \"grid-searching/uncontrolled-mode\", \"showThemeSelector\": true })</p>\n<h3 id=\"controlled-mode\"><a href=\"#controlled-mode\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Controlled Mode</h3>\n<p>In the <a href=\"controlled-and-uncontrolled-modes.md\">controlled mode</a>, pass the search option to the <code>SearchState</code> plugin's <code>value</code> property and handle the <code>onValueChange</code> event to control the search state externally.</p>\n<p>.embedded-demo({ \"path\": \"grid-searching/controlled-mode\", \"showThemeSelector\": true })</p>\n<h2 id=\"remote-searching\"><a href=\"#remote-searching\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Remote Searching</h2>\n<p>You can perform searching remotely by handling search value changes, generating a request, and sending it to the server.</p>\n<p>Searching options are updated once an end user modifies the text in a Search Panel editor or other searching control. Handle search value changes using the <code>SearchState</code> plugin's <code>onValueChange</code> event and request data from the server using the applied searching options. Once the search data is received from the server, pass it to the <code>Grid</code> component's <code>rows</code> property.</p>\n<p>NOTE: Do not use the <code>IntegratedFiltering</code> plugin for remote searching.</p>\n<p>.embedded-demo({ \"path\": \"grid-searching/remote-mode\", \"showThemeSelector\": true })</p>","fields":{"technology":"react/grid","section":"docs"},"frontmatter":{"title":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"react/grid/docs/guides/searching/"}}